<<<<<System requirements>>>>> Before running this container, ensure your system meets the following requirements.

        Apptainer / Singularity runtime
        Linux x86_64 architecture

        No GPU required — this container is CPU-only by design

        Minimum 4GB RAM (8GB+ recommended for larger tabular datasets)
        Minimum 6GB free disk space for container and cache

